&lt;p&gt;Beaverton&#39;s prime location offers easy access to Portland’s cultural attractions, including art galleries, theaters, and live music venues. You’re also less than two hours from the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Oregon Coast&lt;/strong&gt;, the stunning&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Columbia River Gorge&lt;/strong&gt;, and the iconic&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Mount Hood&lt;/strong&gt;, making weekend getaways effortless.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
